Interface PersistentUUIDManager

All Known Implementing Classes:
PersistentUUIDManagerImpl
public interface PersistentUUIDManager
PersistentUUIDManager maintains a mapping of UUIDs present in the cluster
Since:
9.0
Author:
Tristan Tarrant
